info on static cross-compiling from macOS to linux:
https://chr4.org/blog/2017/03/15/cross-compile-and-link-a-static-binary-on-macos-for-linux-with-cargo-and-rust/

remove the passphrase on the ssh key to the remote server

--server: connection to the sftp server including username. if no username is
          found, the server will parse $USER from the env.
--split: how to split the sftp url to find the actual file path on the server

example invocation:
plex-downloader --server "user@derp.biz" --split "roy_rogers/" --port 4567
